  <TITLE>Unobvious search behavior in admin area when &lt;Ignore option &quot;limit per store&quot; rules&gt; option enabled</TITLE>
  <DESCRIPTION>nopCommerce version: 4.10 For example: on the &quot;Products&quot; page we try to search all product limitation to specific store, but if the &lt;Ignore option &quot;limit per store&quot; rules&gt; option enabled, this filter isn't working. I suggest hiding this filter on all pages that contain this search field when this setting is enabled Also note that it's ignored not for all entities. For example, it'll work fine for product reviews and orders</DESCRIPTION>
